类 CRect

java.lang.Object
org.kelvinizer.shapes.CShape
org.kelvinizer.shapes.CRect
所有已实现的接口:
Drawable
public class CRect extends CShape
Represents a rectangle shape with customizable position, size, and origin. Extends the CShape class and provides specific implementation for converting to a Rectangle and scaling the rectangle.
